title: Elvis Presley - It's Midnight (FTD) FLAC
description: This time the focus is on August 1974. Unfortunately the show isn't complete, as the producers explain in the notes that's because the average show in August 1974 was too long for a tape. The tape of this particular show from the 24th (Midnight) ran out after 'If You Talk In Your Sleep' and therefore the producers decided to complete it with a part of the August 29 Dinner Show for the 'complete concert' experience. The show itself is pretty good. - See more at: http://www.elvis.com.a
